Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.mesosfer.MesosferQuery.getUserQuery()
    Please use MesosferUser.getQuery() instead.
    com.mesosfer.MesosferObject.refresh()
    Please use MesosferObject.fetch() instead.
    com.mesosfer.MesosferObject.refreshInBackground(RefreshCallback)
    Please use MesosferObject.fetchInBackground(GetCallback) instead.
    com.mesosfer.MesosferPush.setPushToAndroid(boolean)
    Please use MesosferPush.setQuery(MesosferQuery) with a MesosferQuery targeting MesosferInstallations with a constraint on the deviceType field. If you use #setPushToAndroid(boolean) or MesosferPush.setPushToIOS(boolean), then you will only be able to send to one of these two device types (e.g. and not Windows).
    com.mesosfer.MesosferPush.setPushToIOS(boolean)
    Please use MesosferPush.setQuery(MesosferQuery) with a MesosferQuery targeting MesosferInstallations with a constraint on the deviceType field. If you use #setPushToIOS(boolean) or MesosferPush.setPushToAndroid(boolean), then you will only be able to send to one of these two device types (e.g. and not Windows).
    com.mesosfer.MesosferAnalytics.trackAppOpened(Intent)
    Please use MesosferAnalytics.trackAppOpenedInBackground(Intent) instead.
    com.mesosfer.MesosferAnalytics.trackEvent(String)
    Please use MesosferAnalytics.trackEventInBackground(String) instead.
    com.mesosfer.MesosferAnalytics.trackEvent(String, Map<String, String>)
    Please use MesosferAnalytics.trackEventInBackground(String, Map) instead.
